headline: Quarterra Group Announces Leasing at Emblem Mill Road Apartments
summary: Quarterra Group, a subsidiary of Lennar Corporation and a real estate investment and development firm, today announced the start of leasing at Emblem Mill Road, an attainably priced community located in McDonough, Georgia, southeast of Atlanta. The management of Emblem Mill Road will fall under the recent merger agreement between Quarterra Living, the property management division of Quarterra Group and RKW Residential, the property management arm for Alfred.
